        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3429266351" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4399471968990803411">The collection started off strong, but racism struck in &quot;The Gong of Gods.&quot; It&apos;s real bad, friends. I strongly recommend the newer BBC show instead, as it deals with tough issues gracefully and with nuance.</span>
  <span id="freeText4399471968990803411" style="display:none">The collection started off strong, but racism struck in "The Gong of Gods." It's real bad, friends. I strongly recommend the newer BBC show instead, as it deals with tough issues gracefully and with nuance.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4399471968990803411" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

